videos.description: Paschal Chukwu catches the inbounds pass, makes a move, and jams for Syracuse.
videos.headline: Chukwu dunks off of inbounds pass

videos.description: Frank Howard beats the shot clock for a three-pointer to add to Syracuse's lead.
videos.headline: Howard beats the buzzer for 3

videos.description: Frank Howard hits a deep three to add to Syracuse's lead.
videos.headline: Howard hits long 3-pointer

videos.description: Rickey McGill banks in a three as the shot clock expires to draw Iona closer.
videos.headline: McGill hits a 3-pointer off glass

videos.description: Zach Lewis scores on an athletic layup with and-1 to pull Iona with one of Syracuse late in the first half.
videos.headline: Lewis acrobatic layup and-1 pulls Iona closer

videos.description: Ricky McGill hits a deep three to pull Iona within five early in the second half.
videos.headline: McGill hits a set shot 3

videos.description: Tyus Battle drives the length of the floor and scores and-1 for Syracuse.
videos.headline: Battle goes coast-to-coast for and-1 layup

videos.description: On the fast break, TK Edogi dunks off the alley-oop from Rickey McGill.
videos.headline: Edogi with a nasty fast-break dunk off the alley oop
